A KILLER <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Murder" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Murder" target="_blank">murdered</a> a <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prostitution" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prostitution" target="_blank">prostitute</a> in his home  then <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rape" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rape" target="_blank">raped</a> two other <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vice" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vice" target="_blank">vice</a> girls in <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Front_organization" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Front_organization" target="_blank">front</a> of his <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Death" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Death" target="_blank">dead</a> victimSteven Mathieson carried out the horrendous attacks while his partner was on a night out  and his four <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Year" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Year" target="_blank">year</a> old son was sleeping in the next roomThe car salesman <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stabbing" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stabbing" target="_blank">stabbed</a> tragic Luciana Maurer a <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Total_war" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Total_war" target="_blank">total</a> of 44 <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Times" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Times" target="_blank">times</a> after arranging to meet her at his family home in Falkirk last DecemberHe then went on to <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rape" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rape" target="_blank">rape</a> two other escorts he called to his home that night  and they only escaped by fleeing his <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/House" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/House" target="_blank">house</a> nakedMathieson <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Today_%28NBC_program%29" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Today_%28NBC_program%29" target="_blank">today</a> <a h